2311 Repeat threads
Make sure that only the methods of the Solution class are called in the someActions method.
The expected output in the main method:
Amigo: Mmmmm, beef
Amigo: knock knock
Amigo: Zzzzzzz ... 1 sec

Requirements:
1. The output to the screen should correspond to the condition of the task.
2. In the someActions method, the sleep method of the Solution class must be called.
3. The Solution field must have a name field.
4. In the Solution class, the food field must be present.
5. The Solution field must have a sound field.